1
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:05,080
Are you thirsty or afraid to drink?

2
00:01:10,240 --> 00:01:11,640
You don't want to drink?

3
00:01:11,960 --> 00:01:13,560
I'll punish you.

4
00:01:18,240 --> 00:01:19,039
Sir,

5
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:21,480
All the bandits ambushed outside the city have been caught.

6
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,080
We are waiting for your order.

7
00:01:23,320 --> 00:01:23,760
OK.

8
00:01:25,440 --> 00:01:28,080
Master Chen, you didn’t make peace.

9
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:31,840
and poisoned the well.

10
00:01:32,080 --> 00:01:32,759
Do you know your punishment?

11
00:01:32,759 --> 00:01:33,759
Cut the crap.

12
00:01:38,960 --> 00:01:39,759
My lord.

13
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:42,479
This...

14
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,759
Jiang Manyue, let’s go.

15
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,600
What do you mean?

16
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:52,479
You want to poison the whole village?

17
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:54,320
He doesn't deserve to be my brother.

18
00:01:57,039 --> 00:01:58,240
Come on.

19
00:01:58,240 --> 00:01:59,400
Come on.

20
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,160
Go to hell!

21
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:02,640
Go after him!

22
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,640
Okay.

23
00:02:04,320 --> 00:02:05,520
You traitor!

24
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:07,920
Stop!

25
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:10,680
My lord. My lord.

26
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:12,080
Sir, this...

27
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,560
Take him away.

28
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:14,920
Yes, my lord.

29
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:16,640
Take them away.

30
00:02:16,640 --> 00:02:17,440
Take him away.

31
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:20,120
Ma'am.

32
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:22,320
I'm going back to my second brother.

33
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,440
I'm afraid he'll be in danger.

34
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:26,640
Honey, I'm back.

35
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:32,000
Brother, what's wrong?

36
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:34,920
It's all thanks to Mr. Xiao.

37
00:02:34,920 --> 00:02:35,720
Let me tell you.

38
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,280
Mr. Xiao

39
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:41,200
is a complete mess.

40
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:43,640
But he has good foresight.

41
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:48,720
Magistrate

42
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:51,680
We sinners are at your disposal.

43
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,880
Li Renyi,

44
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:57,200
You’ve never hurt Gusu County.

45
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:59,440
As for Jiang Manyue,

46
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:02,320
you can tell right from wrong.

47
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:06,440
I will turn a blind eye

48
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:08,720
and let you off the hook.

49
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:12,920
You two go back to the mountain and gather your brothers.

50
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:15,160
Pack up and dismiss.

51
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:15,640
But...

52
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:16,800
I know what you want to say.

53
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:19,240
Can you make a living in the future?

54
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:19,720
It doesn't matter.

55
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:22,720
You can buy good fields here.

56
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:23,640
Farming

57
00:03:23,640 --> 00:03:25,200
Self-sufficient

58
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:27,160
Thank you, Magistrate

59
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:28,360
Get up.

60
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:31,400
Xiao Bai.

61
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,240
How did you save them?

62
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,720
Well...

63
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:40,240
Of course, I'll use reason to make you fall in love.

64
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:43,200
It's mainly because I'm elegant.

65
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,760
by my temperament.

66
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,720
Do you want to get beaten up?

67
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:48,320
Honey.

68
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:49,240
Come here!

69
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:50,240
Come here!

70
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,480
Waiter, a bottle of wine.

71
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:18,560
Boss, some signature dishes.

72
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:19,880
Coming.

73
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:23,960
What flavor do you like?

74
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:27,120
Did you forget what I like?

75
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,960
Nameless, why are you here?

76
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:33,640
I've been looking for you.

77
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:37,880
You two...

78
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,840
That's enough.

79
00:04:46,159 --> 00:04:47,760
He hit you first.

80
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:49,400
Who is he?

81
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:50,280
So fierce.

82
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:52,000
Nameless, this is your sister-in-law.

83
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,640
Sister-in-law.

84
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,360
Eat slowly.

85
00:04:59,080 --> 00:04:59,880
Have some water.

86
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:06,200
So...

87
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,240
you're married.

88
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:10,160
you're still a practitioner.

89
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,360
Does your family know?

90
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,280
Lower your voice.

91
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,560
Got it.

92
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:16,480
By the way,

93
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:18,320
When did you get married?

94
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,400
A few days ago.

95
00:05:21,280 --> 00:05:22,360
How did you find me?

96
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:24,360
I know you're in Gusu County.

97
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:27,440
A few nights ago when you went on patrol,

98
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,920
They called you Xiao Bai.

99
00:05:31,840 --> 00:05:32,720
Shut up.

100
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:34,920
Got it.

101
00:05:38,159 --> 00:05:39,040
Understand what?

102
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,480
Nothing.

103
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:46,960
What's the name of this knife?

104
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:47,880
So pretty.

105
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:48,760
Nameless.

106
00:05:48,840 --> 00:05:49,640
Just like me.

107
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:50,920
and unique.

108
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,840
You're good at pretending.

109
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:55,880
Bai.

110
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:57,600
Why didn't you tell me

111
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:59,440
you had such a brother?

112
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:02,600
I don't know about your family background.

113
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:04,680
You're cheating.

114
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,480
I lost my memory.

115
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:10,480
How dare you marry an unknown woman?

116
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,280
You don't understand.

117
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:16,520
You don't need a reason to love someone.

118
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:19,440
You're just saying that.

119
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:21,920
All right.

120
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:24,120
Brother, we haven't seen each other for so long.

121
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:25,920
I've been here for a few days.

122
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:28,400
you two can't take me out to play.

123
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,320
I want to see

124
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:32,640
what this county

125
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,760
that makes you linger?

126
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:42,680
Gusu County is quite interesting.

127
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,480
Right?

128
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:45,560
Especially that place.

129
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,560
This is a good place.

130
00:06:48,159 --> 00:06:52,000
Brother, do you believe someone is eavesdropping on us?

131
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:54,600
Who is it?

132
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:57,280
Stop pretending. How can you not know?

133
00:06:57,520 --> 00:06:59,560
My sister-in-law, your wife.

134
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:02,480
I was forced to marry her.

135
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:04,600
Do you like her?

136
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:09,240
I see.

137
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:12,840
I think she cares about you.

138
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:15,200
No.

139
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,520
She has no feelings for me.

140
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,600
She's warm-hearted.

141
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:20,960
She treats everyone the same.

142
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,440
She treats you differently.

143
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:26,880
Don't you see that she treats you differently?

144
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:32,520
But her identity...

145
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:34,880
her identity.

146
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,440
We'll see.

147
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:36,919
Xiao Bai.

148
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:40,200
