149
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,320
I can't sleep.

150
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:47,920
Is something bothering you?

151
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:50,640
I don't know.

152
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:54,280
It must be because of the hot weather.

153
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:55,280
and annoying.

154
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:58,600
Your brother is so skilled.

155
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,560
