156
00:09:02,920 --> 00:09:04,200
He likes martial arts.

157
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:06,200
I like studying.

158
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:08,560
Isn't it perfect that we're both civil and military?

159
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:13,600
Okay.

160
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:16,640
You two are quite different.

161
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:20,160
If I know martial arts,

162
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:22,640
